videos.description: Zhaire Smith's relentless effort on the boards pays off with a tip-in bucket to increase the lead.
videos.headline: Texas Tech's Smith relentless on the boards and scores athletic tip-in

videos.description: Niem Stevenson hits a 3-pointer as the clock expires to give the Red Raiders a huge lead at the half.
videos.headline: Texas Tech's Stevenson rainbows a 3-pointer at the buzzer

videos.description: Mark Vital muscles through the Texas Tech defense and scores a two-handed layup for the Bears.
videos.headline: Baylor's Vital gets the roll for layup

videos.description: Niem Stevenson steals the pass, drives the court and scores a left-handed layup for the Red Raiders.
videos.headline: Texas Tech's Stevenson picks the pocket and makes the layup

videos.description: Norense Odiase finds Zhaire Smith for a slam dunk to give the Red Raiders its largest lead.
videos.headline: Texas Tech's Smith dunks it in with authority

videos.description: King McClure shot the gap and steals the ball, and slams home the pumpkin for the Bears.
videos.headline: Baylor's McClure with steal and slam
